    "body": "Hey @Olshansk, you are right, they use web3 for historic reasons. Feel free to send a PR.\r\n\r\nRegarding 2, you can set their balance with `config.networks.hardhat.accounts`. You can read more about it here: https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/reference/#config -- Note that we don't use github issues for support questions though.\r\n\r\nI'm closing this issue, but if you send the PR will review it and merge it.\r\n\r\nThanks",
